urlText: Opal can be used between Wollongong and Moss Vale, Exeter and Bundanoon stations.
content:

If travelling onto Goulburn, or other Opal enabled station along the Southern Highlands Line, you should not tap off when transferring from Coach to an Intercity train but instead tap off at your destination station.

Booking is not required for Opal customers on this route.

urlText: Westmead T-way, temporary bus stop closure
content:
From 1am to 4am on Saturday 30 and Sunday 31 October 2021, work for Parramatta Light Rail will result in the following closures:
  • Westmead Hospital, North West T-way (2145559) will be closed.
    A temporary stop will be available on Darcy Rd eastbound for the 665 towards Parramatta.
  • Westmead Hospital, North West T-way (2145560) will be closed.
    A temporary stop will be available on Darcy Rd westbound for the 665 towards Rouse Hill.
Signage will be in place to guide customers.
subtitle: Westmead T-way, temporary bus stop closure

urlText: Henry Lawson Reserve, Blues Point, temporary bus stop closure
content:
From 5am Monday 1 November to 5am Saturday 18 December 2021, Sydney Metro work at Blues Point will result in the temporary closure of bus stop Henry Lawson Reserve (206037) and affect the 254 route towards Riverview and the 291 route towards Epping.

The alternative, temporary bus stop will be available 20 metres east of the current stop.
subtitle: Henry Lawson Reserve, Blues Point, temporary bus stop closure

urlText: L1 Dulwich Hill Line full closure
content:
From 6am Thursday 28 October to 11pm Sunday 31 October, buses will replace L1 Dulwich Hill Line light rail services between Central Grand Concourse and Dulwich Hill, due to operational issues.

See the Transport news story for planned replacement bus frequency, recommended capacity and stops locations.

Night services between Central Grand Concourse and The Star continue to be suspended.

L2 Randwick Line and L3 Kingsford Line will continue to run as per normal schedule.

Normal full light rail services will resume at 6am Monday 01 November.

Please allow extra travel time and use the Trip Planner or check travel alerts to see if you travel is affected.
subtitle: L1 Dulwich Hill Line full closure

urlText: Temporary service changes at Customs House, Watt St

Visit newcastletransport.info for more information.
